reviews.comments:
Pros:
- easy access to the apartment which was very clean and bright, in good order, with air-conditioned;
- modern kitchen with dishwasher, comfortable bedroom and living room;
- owner easy to reach and attentive (accomodated a late departure).
Cons:
- lack of equipment in kitchen (only one saucepan available, no strainer, lack of container for leftovers), very small bathroom.
